edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks

Class ClassBreaksDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks.ClassificationDefinition
        • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks.ClassBreaksDefinition

  • public class ClassBreaksDefinition
extends ClassificationDefinition
    Class added v2.6 Define a class breaks classification scheme used by the GenerateDataTask to generate classes. Class breaks renderers symbolize data based on the value of a numeric attribute. Data with similar values for the attribute use the same symbol.
    Author:
    Justin Merz
